data.description: Don’t miss the opportunity to own this charming Cape Cod in sought after Glenwood.  This home boasts recent updates and its own private oasis with a swimming pool, a pergola with a retractable canopy, a vegetable garden, patio and fire pit surrounded by a 6 ft privacy fence.  Enter the bright and airy living room highlighting updated, wide-plank laminate flooring is highlighted on the main level.  The kitchen features a new top-of-the-line LG Instaview stainless refrigerator and offers access to the backyard.  Conveniently located on the entry level are two sizable bedrooms with updated flooring and a full bath.  The upper level provides two additional bedrooms showcasing beautiful, refinished hardwood flooring and a laundry room.   Enjoy outdoor living in your own private oasis and living in this excellent location with convenient major commuter routes, nearby BWI airport, and Annapolis, Baltimore, Columbia and Arundel Mills, Marley Station Mall provide a variety of restaurants, shopping centers and recreational options.
